channel.title: Looking for some help returning to Private Servers
channel.description:
Hello everyone, It's been quite awhile since I've been using Java code and private servers. I'm hoping to find a person who has enough experience to help me out, 1 on 1, and see if I can relearn it faster than usual.
My main goal is to find a completely empty base and bring it up into a very interactive server, much like those today. Most of the coding will become more clearer as we discuss back and forth about it, since I've led plenty of servers back in the day.(Back when it was.. DK 6 and Update 10 or so :P)
Just send me a message or reply on here, I'd love to get a tutor to help me out return into Private servers.
Thanks.
